**The city stretches vertically, with towering skyscrapers touching the clouds. The buildings are made of modern and futuristic materials, with tempered glass and shiny metal. Huge digital screens are scattered throughout the buildings, displaying advertisements and rapidly changing high-definition images. The streets are full of autonomous flying vehicles that move at high speed on separate tracks in the air. They come in different shapes and sizes, some look like small drones while others are the size of buses. The city is teeming with advanced technologies, from smart streetlamps that automatically adjust to ambient lighting to robots that perform everyday tasks on streets and buildings. The townspeople use cybernetic implants to communicate, transact financially and access information instantly. The parks and squares are green oases in the middle of the city, with huge trees and exotic plants growing in vertical gardens and suspended terraces. People gather in public spaces to relax, socialize and take in incredible views of the futuristic city. The city has a bustling and vibrant atmosphere, with an eclectic mix of cultures, languages ​​and lifestyles. There is a sense of optimism and constant progress as new technologies and innovations emerge every day, making life easier and more exciting for city dwellers.** - Upscaled by <@682018457415581751> (fast)
